@ihorlukianov , does this change affect the upgrade ?

@payert all the existing clusters will use old primary key. To use the fixed one the table needs to be deleted. 
Currently this issue affects only Nifi grafana graphs. The root cause that led to finding this issue is false metrics that should be fixed in other task. Once it's fixed the old PK should be fine for all graphs.
